%hive
-- Every tripâ€™s aggregated features at a trip id level.
--
SELECT deaccel_event_cnt.trip_id,
    deaccel_event_cnt.ft_count_vehicle_deaccel_val,
    hard_brake_10_cnt.ft_sum_hard_brakes_10_flg_val,
    hard_brake_3_cnt.ft_sum_hard_brakes_3_flg_val
FROM (
    SELECT trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_count_vehicle_deaccel_val
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, acceleration_group
        FROM drive_temp
        GROUP BY trip_id, acceleration_group
        HAVING MIN(acceleration) < 0
    ) deaccel_event
    GROUP BY trip_id
) deaccel_event_cnt
JOIN
(
    SELECT trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_sum_hard_brakes_10_flg_val
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, acceleration_group
        FROM drive_temp
        GROUP BY trip_id, acceleration_group
        HAVING MIN(acceleration) <= -10
    ) hard_break_10
    GROUP BY trip_id
) hard_brake_10_cnt
ON deaccel_event_cnt.trip_id = hard_brake_10_cnt.trip_id
JOIN
(
    SELECT trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_sum_hard_brakes_3_flg_val
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, acceleration_group, MIN(acceleration) AS min_acceleration
        FROM drive_temp
        GROUP BY trip_id, acceleration_group
        HAVING MIN(acceleration) <= -3 AND MIN(acceleration) > -10
    ) hard_break_3
    GROUP BY trip_id
) hard_brake_3_cnt
ON deaccel_event_cnt.trip_id = hard_brake_3_cnt.trip_id
JOIN
(
    SELECT trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_sum_time_deaccel_val
    FROM (
        SELECT trip_id, acceleration, acceleration_group
        FROM drive_temp
        WHERE acceleration < 0
    ) sum_deaccel
    GROUP BY trip_id
) sum_deaccel_cnt
ON deaccel_event_cnt.trip_id = sum_deaccel_cnt.trip_id
ORDER BY trip_id
